**Openlegend Dice Commands**

```/roll [flags] [attribute] [advantage] [quantity]```
```/r [flags] [attribute] [advantage] [quantity]```    
Flags:
-R: Repeat the roll  
-V: Vicious Strike: Exploding dice have advantage 
-D: Destructive Trance: Explode on max or one less

**Raw Dice Commands**

```/!r [xdice pattern]``` 
```/!roll [xdice pattern]```
xdice pattern: Given pattern should be as described in the xdice documentation: https://xdice.readthedocs.io/en/latest/dice_notation.html#patterns. Use this to roll "raw", i.e. without any Openlegend RPG specific logic.